text:
I rarely came across hotels that consistently provides excellent service from the time when entered all the way until check out. Often, parts of the service elements may let down the others. 
But this hotel is definitely a rarity. 
I was really impressed by its stylish interior design, pleasant check in experience, helpful employees, excellent room interior, and great overnight sleep.
In fact, thanks to its carpeted floor, it gave me a sense of homey feeling, which makes my overnight sleep in here one of the most pleasant I've ever had. 
Even the breakfast menu was excellent and well varied too.
If there's something lacking was the fact that I only stayed in here for one night only. I wish if I could get additional night. 
Would I willing to return back to here again? Of course! Although, I can't be certain when. 
Overall, I would rate my stay in this hotel 5 out of 5. 
If TripAdvisor gave options for 7 stars, I would click that one because this hotel truly exceeding my expectations!
title: Definitel The Best Sleep in Recent Times

first of all, the location is great, easily accessible. the check in process was fast. the room was clean and well maintained. breakfast menu was really delicious and have vast array of choices.

a bit of inconvenience was when I stayed there, there was loud live music on the restaurant below and the sound was heard from our room (our room was on 7th floor, imagine how loud it is for the lower level room)

title: great stay, nice hotel

text:
This is my 2nd stay after 2 weeks ago I also stayed in this hotel. Some notes from my 1st visit didn't get any improve. Hotel location quite OK but the security infront of hotel didn't help at all to pass through the car to the main street and they just standing infront of lobby doing nothing! This is very bad and this stay I also experience the same thing again. They also didn't provide welcome drink at all , as I believe as 4star plus rated (as they claimed) they should consider to provide welcome drink. Breakfast taste was flat and 3 days stay I experienced similar breakfast menu and seems there is no menu rotation. . The only department who helpful a lot is Housekeeping department, they were very fast response and helpful. If they want me to become they repeat customer, they should understand and follow to guest request. I only ask late check out till 2 pm as my train was at 8 pm and they only allow me to stay until 12.30 noon even though I checked myself at online booking the availability room still huge and they offered cheaper lowest rate, it means they lied to me by saying sorry we are running high occupancy and only allow 30 minutes late check out!!!!
I will fully reconsider again if I want to stay in this hotel again after the treatment I received after my 2nd stay within 2 weeks. Forgot to mention also  they don't have actually good facilities like swimming pool , it is very small and location on the corner of 2nd floor and smell smoking! Very bad !
title: There is no special attention to Repeat Customer!

text:
I spend my weekend here .
LOBBY: the lobby is a comfort, check in was with ease as I was checked in within 5 minutes. (excellent reception)
ROOM: The room was also spacious and very clean and room bigger than most rooms in Jogja and for this price, it can't go wrong and you can't find it anywhere else. The water pressure in the shower was strong and they also have a 'rain shower' facility. The bed was EXTREMELY comfortable.

If you need good and friendly transportation at Yogyakarta you just very easy to find Yogyakarta Asmaradhana tour and travel at TripAdvisor or Google map.

All in all, it was a great stay in this brand  hotel and I'll definitely stay at this hotel again in the future
title: GREAT SERVICES

text: The hotel rooms are satisfactory because they are very clean and tidy. The facilities provided are very good to its customers to make their customers comfortable.  We can have breakfast at the rooftop restaurant with a beautiful city view.  Not only that, our breakfast is also served with a delicious and varied menu.  The service at the hotel suites bianti is very friendly. our family is comfortable and satisfied staying at hotel suites bianti.  Highly recommended for tourists or anyone who wants to stay at HOTEL SUITES BIANTI.
title: Comfortable Room

text:
Rebranding hotel. The hotel was previously named Aston (info from receptionist on duty). Located on the main road which is very busy and strategic. Easy come and easy go. Walking distance for food and mini market. The check-in process is quite simple and fast. we ordered 2 rooms with connecting but after entering the room it turned out that the door was still locked so we had to wait again to be opened. Property  and room design still seem not updated. Bathroom amenities  very complete. 
The breakfast menu is limited varians. The buffet menu ran out and it was too late for filled again. Thank you for Ms. Desvita who has served very friendly and kind.
Housekeeping service needs to be improved again. we asked for extra soap the wait was quite long while we had to prepare to check out. In general the service of this hotel is ordinary
title: Hotel with Strategic Location

text:
The room is very clean and tidy, this hotel profide coffe maker at the room so I can make fresh coffee by my self. Is an excellent choice to stay, the breakfast was served in the roft top restaurant with nice city view. All the menu so good and various. The staff so friendly 
Can't wait to see new design of Artotel Suites Bianti
title: My Staycation

text: had a superb comfy short escape here. staff was incredibly helpful, and the amenities were great. room was spacious and clean. breakfast menu were various and sooooo good. surely will make up ur day...!
title: short escape

text: Step on your feet and enter this hotel, the hotel is very spacious, clean and tidy interior arrangement. Although it is a transition period from the previous hotel. But in terms of interior and exterior, everything is still good. Walking to the elevator, you can see that there is a bianti boutique, there are Javanese batiks that have good and neat materials. Keep walking towards the elevator again. it looks like there is a big light supporting the 2nd floor decorated with a very magnificent grand piano. Upon entering the lift, very luxurious with helpful hints. The rooms here are very spacious, clean and tidy. what amazed me, here they use a coffee maker from Nespresso from Nescafé. And Amenities using Natasha skincare products, ranging from soap, shampoo, conditioner to very fragrant body lotion. Here there are also many facilities, ranging from swimming pools, gyms, saunas to spas and massages. Very happy to be able to stay and spend the night at this hotel. From all aspects, it is very satisfying and has a very strategic location in the middle of the city of Jogja, close to a shopping center. at last but not least. I am happy and very satisfied.
title: My Staycation Trips

text:
A city center hotel that has complete facilities and very delicious restaurant with a varied menu. Highly recomended for a family vacation.
The room was nice and comfortable with great amenities. Staffs are all great, friendly and very helpful as well.
title: Holiday

text: This hotel is an excellent choice to stay for a short getaway from the chaos of our daily routines. The room was nice and comfortable with great amenities. The breakfast was served in the top floor restaurant with nice city view. And every menu was so good! Staffs are all great,  friendly and very helpful as well. So, thank you!
title: Great hotel!

text: It is a well stay with spacious room and luxury room amenities. Good food and good ambiance with some contemporary artwork to be installed to show the legendary of Yogyakarta as a culture city in a modern way.
title: A new luxury artsy hotel in Yogyakarta
